      "description": "The validated operating envelope is bounded as follows: axial compressive load 0–2500 N; bending moment 0–25 N·m; crosshead displacement rate 1–5 mm/min; screw outer diameter 7.3–7.7 mm (manufacturing tolerance ±0.2 mm); screw length 40–55 mm; UHMWPE block modulus 900–1100 MPa; titanium alloy Ti-6Al-4V with yield strength 880–950 MPa; ambient temperature 20–25 °C; single-level construct geometry per ASTM F1717 fixture. All 11 experimental constructs and all FEA ensemble runs fall within these bounds."
