      "description": "Results apply exclusively to non-cannulated solid-core pedicle screws with outer diameter 7.3–7.7 mm and length 40–55 mm, fabricated from Ti-6Al-4V ELI per ASTM F136, tested under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending protocol. Cannulated designs, screws outside the stated diameter or length range, alternative alloys (e.g., CoCr, PEEK), dynamic fatigue loading, and multi-level constructs are outside this applicability domain and require separate V&V activities."
    }
